msgid "gluon-config-mode:welcome"
msgstr ""
"<p>Welcome to the setup wizard of your new Freifunk-Darmstadt node.</"
"p><p>Please choose a hostname that follows the pattern &lt;ZIP&gt;-&lt;"
"fantasyname&gt; (e.g. 64289-unicorn), where ZIP refers to the postal code "
"at the location the node is going to be set up at and fantasyname can be "
"freely chosen.</p><p>In case you want to limit the bandwidth used for the "
"mesh vpn, please note that at least 100 kBit/s are necessary, because of "
"the base load (ca. 30kBit/s) each router generates.</p>"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:pubkey"
msgstr ""
"<p>This is the public key of your Freifunk node. Only after it has been "
"deployed on the servers of Freifunk Darmstadt, the router can connect to "
"the mesh-vpn. Therefore please send its name (<em><%=escape(hostname)%></em>) and "
"public key to <a href=\"mailto:keys@darmstadt.freifunk.net?"
"subject=Registration:%20<%=urlescape(hostname)%>&amp;body=%23%20<%=urlescape(hostname)%>%0A"
"%23%20<%=sysconfig.primary_mac%>%0Akey%20%22<%=pubkey%>%22%3B"
"\">keys@darmstadt.freifunk.net</a>.</p>"
"<div class=\"the-key\">"
" # <%= escape(hostname) %><br />"
" # <%= sysconfig.primary_mac %><br />"
"key \"<%= pubkey %>\";"
"</div>"

msgid "gluon-config-mode:reboot"
msgstr ""
"<p>Your node is currently restarting and afterwards will try to connect to "
"Freifunk nodes nearby. More information regarding your local Freifunk "
"community can be found on <a href=\"https://darmstadt.freifunk.net\">our "
"website</a>.</p><p>Thank you for running a node and have fun exploring the "
"world of Freifunk!</p>"
